  "3093160": {
    "name": "INTERSCAPE",
    "steam_appid": 3093160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/9ff79b1474dcda612967e8f5bcdee980.poster.avif?t=1764573452\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/9ff79b1474dcda612967e8f5bcdee980.webm?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/9ff79b1474dcda612967e8f5bcdee980.mp4?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;梦吞噬了现实&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BlueDot 的“Oracle”梦境机器曾让人类得以体验任何自己渴望的梦。然而某一天，一个巨大的黑色球体突然出现在天空中，将人类的梦想变成无法逃离的噩梦。如今，人们被困在名为“梦”的牢笼之中，无法回到现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有进入他人梦境能力的梦潜者“K”决定直接跳入这座危险的梦境迷宫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/7d762a32103da15dd60a04dbded2e28e.poster.avif?t=1764573452\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/7d762a32103da15dd60a04dbded2e28e.webm?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/7d762a32103da15dd60a04dbded2e28e.mp4?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&lt;INTERSCAPE&gt; 是一款以剧情为核心的动作冒险游戏，以突出的电影化演出呈现探索梦境与现实边界的独特体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;每个梦境，都是新的能力&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个梦境都是独立的世界，由其主人的潜意识编织而成，并蕴藏着等待你掌握的新能力。你可以在两个梦境之间穿梭，操控时间的流动，以挑战看似不可能的谜题。有时，你甚至必须化身为非人类的存在，才能发现那些从未被揭示的真相碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/139d551d90cd150a4fd683620ee7d33d.poster.avif?t=1764573452\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/139d551d90cd150a4fd683620ee7d33d.webm?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/139d551d90cd150a4fd683620ee7d33d.mp4?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;拯救沉睡的世界&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开被神秘黑色球体与无尽梦境困住的人类命运。很明显，如果他们无法醒来，灭绝将不可避免。探索混乱交织的梦境，寻找能够拯救沉睡众生的最终秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/c5c94dad94644fd919652585d3b7f762.poster.avif?t=1764573452\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/c5c94dad94644fd919652585d3b7f762.webm?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/c5c94dad94644fd919652585d3b7f762.mp4?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;梦之世界&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫步于美丽的景观，探索引人入胜的超现实世界。但在美丽之下，危险与噩梦始终潜伏。你必须穿越纠缠的梦境碎片，继续向出口前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/38bdbf266a1cca45c77317da3465241a.poster.avif?t=1764573452\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/38bdbf266a1cca45c77317da3465241a.webm?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/38bdbf266a1cca45c77317da3465241a.mp4?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验 INTERSCAPE 的原创故事、震撼视觉效果与情感音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/dbb7caaf833f95c99913ba1b2281de3f.poster.avif?t=1764573452\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/dbb7caaf833f95c99913ba1b2281de3f.webm?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093160/extras/dbb7caaf833f95c99913ba1b2281de3f.mp4?t=1764573452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
